item.title: CVE-2024-33004|2024-05-14T04:00:25.081Z -- SAP_SE -- SAP BusinessObjects Business Intelligence Platform (Webservices)
item.description: SAP Business Objects Business Intelligence Platform is vulnerable to Insecure Storage as dynamic web pages are getting cached even after logging out. On successful exploitation, the attacker can see the sensitive information through cache and can open the pages causing limited impact on Confidentiality, Integrity and Availability of the application.
